728
01:03:43,201 --> 01:03:46,100
No. No. No. No. No. No!

729
01:03:46,101 --> 01:03:48,500
If you don't have any
issues, then don't contact me.

730
01:03:48,501 --> 01:03:52,100
Tell me honestly. Do you
really like me as a person?

731
01:03:52,101 --> 01:03:54,300
Human hearts change.
That's their specialty.

732
01:03:54,301 --> 01:03:56,100
There's no such thing as forever.

733
01:03:56,101 --> 01:03:58,000
It's a beautiful morning, Han Kang!

734
01:03:58,001 --> 01:04:00,500
For everything up to now, I thank you.

735
01:04:00,501 --> 01:04:01,200
What is this?

736
01:04:01,201 --> 01:04:04,200
I plan to leave this place
and go somewhere far away.

737
01:04:04,201 --> 01:04:06,400
Song Yi Kyung. Song Yi Kyung?

738
